globs: ["**/app/api/**", "**/lib/api*", "**/lib/hooks*"]
---

# MagByte API rules

- External REST API base: https://mag-byte-api.vercel.app/api
- All API calls use Axios instance from /lib/api/ (never raw fetch in components)
- Always handle loading, error, and empty states in queries
- Use TanStack Query queryKeys as arrays: ['resource', id, filters]
- Never put business logic in API route handlers — keep them thin
- Auth token comes from Zustand store — never from localStorage directly in a component
